    "name": "§c§n§lSearing Crescent",
    "description": "You channel energy from your burning heart and surroundings, into your weapon (sword or axe) to then release it in the form of a destructive air slash (takes 30% of your resource bar). Without the aid of a weapon or without enough energy (less than 30%), all the stored energy will release in the form of a smokescreen which may also result in damaging yourself depending on the energy absorbed. The power of your slash will depend on the calorific energy of your surroundings (biome), however, if on a fire source, you will always bring out your maximum output. Furthermore, a knight has pride in its own power but must also acknowledge its own weaknesses, thus it wouldn't be wise to use one's powers in an unfavorable situation. \n\n(Get damaged by trying to use 'Searing Crescent' in water or under rain)"
